modifiers.name: .primary
modifiers.description: Indicates button is the primary action.

modifiers.name: .smaller
modifiers.description: Indicates button is the primary action.

sections.css:
h1
  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)
  font-family: "Lato", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif
  font-size: 1.8em
  margin: 0
  &:hover
    color: #f00
  &.primary
    color: #b00
    font-weight: 400
  &.smaller
    font-size: 0.5em

.doc
  margin: 3em 0
  font-family: "Lato", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif
  font-size: 1.1em
  font-weight: 300
  a
    border: 1px solid white
    border-radius: 3px
    padding: 0.75em 0.7em
    color: white
    text-decoration: none
    transition: color 0.1s linear
    &:hover
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2)
      color: white
      transition: all 0.15s linear

modifiers.name: .primary
modifiers.description: Indicates button is the primary action.

sections.css:
@-webkit-keyframes welcome 
  from
    transform: scale(0)
    opacity: 0

  50%
    transform: scale(0)
    opacity: 0

  82.5%
    transform: scale(1.03)
    animation-timing-function: ease-out
    opacity: 1

  to
    transform: scale(1)
